\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4811225\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 20, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jwc1695725497353.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jwc1695725497353.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jwc1695725497353.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jwc1695725497353\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can use the following default shortcut keys in the IDE to navigate inside the editor\n\t\tor trigger various supported actions with a keyboard, such as compile a current object or\n\t\tcompile and test an object. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__section_w2459ab1b5b1_w2460ab1b5_w2461ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\">You can also modify and define your own shortcut key combinations for the supported\n\t\t\t\tactions in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">[userkeys]</code> section of the\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jwc1695725497353_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__codeblock_kxp_nmc_bzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[userkeys] \nnav.ubar=Alt+D\nnav.message.frame=Ctrl+M\neditor.refresh=F5\neditor.close=Ctrl+F4\neditor.close.all=Ctrl+Shift+F4\neditor.next=Ctrl+Tab\neditor.previous=Ctrl+Shift+Tab\nbuild.compile=Ctrl+F7\nbuild.test=Ctrl+F5\nbuild.compile.test=Ctrl+Shift+F7\ncode.comment=Ctrl+K\ncode.uncomment=Ctrl+Shift+K\ncode.uppercase=Ctrl+U\ncode.lowercase=Ctrl+Shift+U\ncode.formatselection=Alt+F\ncode.formatdocument=Alt+Shift+F\ncode.search=Ctrl+F\ncode.searchandreplace=Ctrl+H\ncode.gotoline=Ctrl+G\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Action-0-0\" id=\"topic-Action-0-0\" name=\"topic-Action-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Action-0-0\">Action</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Default shortcut key combination-1-0\" id=\"topic-Default shortcut key combination-1-0\" name=\"topic-Default shortcut key combination-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Default shortcut key combination-1-0\">Default shortcut key combination</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Usage-2-0\" id=\"topic-Usage-2-0\" name=\"topic-Usage-2-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Usage-2-0\">Usage</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-search\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-search\"></use></svg></button><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">19 rows found</div></div><div><button aria-label=\"Export table to a file\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageTableExportButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-v\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-v\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicPageTableExportMenu\"><button aria-label=\"Export to Excel\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to Excel</button><button aria-label=\"Export to CSV\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to CSV</button></div></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scroll\" data-testid=\"sticky-header-table\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHead\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHeadInner\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; width: 709px; padding-right: 0px;\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"3\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; width: 709px;\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Default keyboard combination's description</span></caption><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\"><th aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" aria-label=\"Action: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 211px;\" tabindex=\"0\">Action</th><th aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" aria-label=\"Default shortcut key combination: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 211px;\" tabindex=\"0\">Default shortcut key combination</th><th aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" aria-label=\"Usage: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 211px;\" tabindex=\"0\">Usage</th></tr>\n<tr class=\"searchTableDiv\"><td><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-Action-0\">Filter</label><input aria-label=\"Filter column\" class=\"zDocsInputField zDocsSearchInTable\" id=\"search-Action-0\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">19 rows found</div></td><td><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-Default shortcut key combination-1\">Filter</label><input aria-label=\"Filter column\" class=\"zDocsInputField zDocsSearchInTable\" id=\"search-Default shortcut key combination-1\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">19 rows found</div></td><td><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-Usage-2\">Filter</label><input aria-label=\"Filter column\" class=\"zDocsInputField zDocsSearchInTable\" id=\"search-Usage-2\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">19 rows found</div></td></tr></thead></table></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scrollBody zDocsScrollBodyDiv\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: auto; width: 100%;\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" style=\"height: 0px;\"><th aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" aria-label=\"Action: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 211px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">Action</div></th><th aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" aria-label=\"Default shortcut key combination: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 211px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">Default shortcut key combination</div></th><th aria-controls=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb\" aria-label=\"Usage: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 211px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">Usage</div></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">nav.ubar</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Alt+D</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To navigate to the main U-Bar. The current U-Bar content is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\talso selected, allowing you to start typing directly.</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">nav.message.frame</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+M</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To move focus to the next message frame</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">editor.refresh</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">F5</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To refresh the current editor window</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">editor.close</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+F4</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To close the current editor tab</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">editor.close.all</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+F4</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To close all editor tabs</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">editor.next</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Tab</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To open the next editor tab</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">editor.previous</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+Tab</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To open the previous editor tab</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">build.compile</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+F7</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To compile the current object</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">build.test</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+F5</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To test the current component</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">build.compile.test</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+F7</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To compile and test the current object</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.comment </kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+K</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To comment out a code </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.uncomment</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+K</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To uncomment out a code</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.uppercase</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+U</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To uppercase a selection of code</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.lowercase</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Ctrl+Shift+U</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To lowercase a selection of code</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.formatselection</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Alt+F</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To format and indent a selection of code</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.formatdocument</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\">Alt+Shift+F</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To format an entire document from the first to the last\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tline</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.search</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\">Ctrl+F</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To search a string in code</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.searchandreplace</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\">Ctrl+H</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To search and replace a string in code</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__1\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">code.gotoline</kbd></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__2\">Ctrl+G</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_omf_qql_xyb__entry__3\">To go to a line number in code</td>\n</tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"dataTables_scrollFoot\" style=\"overflow: hidden; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollFootInner\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"3\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;\"><tfoot></tfoot></table></div></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">IDE Keyboard Shortcuts</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"jwc1695725497353__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/showcase/10552636/video/880535057\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Click to watch or listen IDE Keyboard Shortcuts video\" class=\"image\" id=\"jwc1695725497353__image_kp5_jqw_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sni1710750486960.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[userkeys]</a><p>You can add user-defined keyboard shortcut keys for various Uniface IDE actions or your applications in the [userkeys] section of the usys.ini file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4811225\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4811225\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Adding user-defined keyboard shortcuts in the IDE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 20, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 You can use the following default shortcut keys in the IDE to navigate inside the editor or trigger various supported actions with a keyboard, such as compile a current object or compile and test an object. You can also modify and define your own shortcut key combinations for the supported actions in the [userkeys] section of the usys.ini file. Explain this code [userkeys] nav.ubar=Alt+D nav.message.frame=Ctrl+M editor.refresh=F5 editor.close=Ctrl+F4 editor.close.all=Ctrl+Shift+F4 editor.next=Ctrl+Tab editor.previous=Ctrl+Shift+Tab build.compile=Ctrl+F7 build.test=Ctrl+F5 build.compile.test=Ctrl+Shift+F7 code.comment=Ctrl+K code.uncomment=Ctrl+Shift+K code.uppercase=Ctrl+U code.lowercase=Ctrl+Shift+U code.formatselection=Alt+F code.formatdocument=Alt+Shift+F code.search=Ctrl+F code.searchandreplace=Ctrl+H code.gotoline=Ctrl+G Copy Search: Column Action Default shortcut key combination Usage Filter results... 19 rows found Export to Excel Export to CSV Table 1. Default keyboard combination's description Action Default shortcut key combination Usage Filter 19 rows found Filter 19 rows found Filter 19 rows found Action Default shortcut key combination Usage nav.ubar Alt+D To navigate to the main U-Bar. The current U-Bar content is also selected, allowing you to start typing directly. nav.message.frame Ctrl+M To move focus to the next message frame editor.refresh F5 To refresh the current editor window editor.close Ctrl+F4 To close the current editor tab editor.close.all Ctrl+Shift+F4 To close all editor tabs editor.next Ctrl+Tab To open the next editor tab editor.previous Ctrl+Shift+Tab To open the previous editor tab build.compile Ctrl+F7 To compile the current object build.test Ctrl+F5 To test the current component build.compile.test Ctrl+Shift+F7 To compile and test the current object code.comment Ctrl+K To comment out a code code.uncomment Ctrl+Shift+K To uncomment out a code code.uppercase Ctrl+U To uppercase a selection of code code.lowercase Ctrl+Shift+U To lowercase a selection of code code.formatselection Alt+F To format and indent a selection of code code.formatdocument Alt+Shift+F To format an entire document from the first to the last line code.search Ctrl+F To search a string in code code.searchandreplace Ctrl+H To search and replace a string in code code.gotoline Ctrl+G To go to a line number in code Table 2. Related learning videos Title link IDE Keyboard Shortcuts Related Links [userkeys] You can add user-defined keyboard shortcut keys for various Uniface IDE actions or your applications in the [userkeys] section of the usys.ini file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}